# AI Mock Interview Platform

An AI-powered mock interview platform that helps users practice interviews using
text and voice-based answers with intelligent feedback.

## Features
- Text-based interview questions
- Voice-based answers (Speech-to-Text)
- AI-powered answer evaluation
- Grammar, fluency, and confidence scoring
- Interview history and progress tracking
- Professional dashboard UI

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: Node.js, Express
- AI Engine: Python, Flask, spaCy
- Database: MySQL (or Local Storage for history)

## How to Run
1. Start backend server
2. Start AI engine (Flask)
3. Open frontend in browser

